# Frontend Kore

## Composants charte

| Surface | Composants |
|---------|------------|
| Public | `PublicButton`, `PublicCard`, `PublicInput`, `PublicSection`, `PublicPageHero`, `KoreLogo` |
| App | `AppButton`, `AppCard`, `AppInput`, `AppTable`, `AppBadge`, `AppPageHeader`, `TenantLogo` |
| Mobile | `MobileDrawer`, `AppBottomNav` |

## Layouts

- `layouts/public.vue` — landing, login, tarifs (drawer mobile)
- `layouts/default.vue` — app authentifiée (sidebar desktop, bottom nav + drawer mobile)

## Responsive (obligatoire)

- Breakpoints : mobile ≤768px, desktop ≥900px
- `AppPageHeader` stack vertical ≤640px
- CTAs pleine largeur mobile
- Safe area : `env(safe-area-inset-bottom)` sur bottom nav

## Logo

Variant `hero` = PNG source (`/brand/kore-logo-hero.png`).
